          </h2>
          <p class={`${responsive.text.p} text-white mb-6 pc:mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto opacity-90`}>
            お客様のご来店をお待ちしております。お気軽にお問い合わせください。
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a 
              href="tel:03-1234-5678"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 pc:px-8 pc:py-4 bg-white text-brown rounded-lg font-bold text-base pc:text-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105"
            >
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"></path>
              </svg>
              03-1234-5678
            </a>
            <a 
              href="/contact"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 pc:px-8 pc:py-4 border-2 border-white text-white rounded-lg font-bold text-base pc:text-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white hover:text-brown hover:scale-105"
